{
  "id": "adv_event_2404_02_02",
  "title": "魚魚っと\n社長の方針",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――魚魚っとさんが社長になってからしばらくして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Some time after Gyogyo-tto-san became president",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.5341843843,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "なんで私達オリジナルグッズの製作なんて\nさせられてるのかしら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are we being made to produce\noriginal merchandise…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.4666664918,
      "endTime": 8.2103625138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.3999998252
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "「BIGGYOになるためにまずは自分で自分の魅力を\n引き出す練習をするギョ」って言ってたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He said‚ \"To become BIGGYO‚ you need to practice\nbringing out your own charm first‚ gyo.”…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.3999998252,
      "endTime": 16.189274040900003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "分からなくもないけど……そもそも私達が\n自由に作ったグッズなんて売れるのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Somehow I can understand it‚ but…\nWill the goods we made on our own actually sell?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.4333334128,
      "endTime": 23.2931745688,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.5000000794
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02-gyogyo001.m4a",
      "text": "怜ギョン、琴乃ギョン、生配信始めるギョ～！\nGYO～GYO～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-gyo‚ Kotono-gyo‚ it’s time to start the live stream‚ gyo~!\nGYO! GYO!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.5000000794,
      "endTime": 30.5821543534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.0374736785
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん！　こんにちギョー！\n魚見ショッピングの時間だギョ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gyood afternoon‚ everyone!\nIt's time for Gyogyomi Shopping‚ gyo~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.6000014781,
      "endTime": 39.6012258052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.8000014781
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "今日はこころ達がプロデュースした新グッズのお披露目\n配信です～！　じゃんじゃん紹介していきますよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ we’re unveiling the new merchandise that we produced~!\nWe'll be introducing them one after another~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8000014781,
      "endTime": 47.8410898684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "トップバッターは私成宮すずですわ！\nこちらご覧くださいまし、私がデザインした黄金法被！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I‚ Narumiya Suzu‚ will be the first batter!\nPlease take a look at this golden haori I designed!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.0333348114,
      "endTime": 58.047643550100005,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_vanish-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10349.462302699998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.2333337147
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ゴージャスで高貴な私のファンの皆様には\nライブでもこれくらい目立っていただきたいのです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My gorgeous and noble fans\nshould stand out this much even at lives.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.4000065644,
      "endTime": 65.17919023820001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.3666732311
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "これで次のライブで一番目立つのは私と私のファン！\nふふふっ……我ながら天才過ぎるアイデアですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With this‚ my fans and I will be the most noticeable at the next live!\nFufufu… This idea is just so genius‚ even for me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.3666732311,
      "endTime": 76.7580790996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.9666732311
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "凄く派手な法被ね……でもすずらしくて素敵だと思うわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s a very flashy haori… But it suits you and I think it’s wonderful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.9666732311,
      "endTime": 82.868736887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.0666732311
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "やりおーる……こころも負けませんよ！　こころの\n作ったグッズはこころ特製フェイスシールでーす！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pretty good… I won’t lose either! Kokoro’s\nmerchandise is Kokoro’s special face stickers~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.0666732311,
      "endTime": 92.93111777310001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.1333398978
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "可愛いけど、こころが作ったにしては\nなんだか地味な気もするわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re cute‚ but for something Kokoro made‚\nthey seem kind of plain.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.1333398978,
      "endTime": 99.4854033629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.7000065644
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "くくくっ……実はこのフェイスシールただのシール\nじゃないんですよ。特殊な素材で出来てまして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kukuku… Actually‚ these face stickers aren’t just\nordinary stickers. They’re made of a special material.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.7000065644,
      "endTime": 108.2350176652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.4333398978
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、魚魚っと社長さん！\nスタジオの電気消してくれますかー？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ President Gyogyo-tto-san!\nCould you turn off the studio lights~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.4333398978,
      "endTime": 113.3282376448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.5333398978
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02-gyogyo002.m4a",
      "text": "ギョギョッ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gyogyo?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.5333398978,
      "endTime": 114.4421153943,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_switch-01.m4a",
          "delay": 908.7754964999988
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "わぁっ！？　こころちゃんの顔が光ってる！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa!? Kokoro-chan's face is glowing!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.9000024955,
      "endTime": 118.78242880510001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.8824288051
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "蓄光素材なんです～！　こころのファンがみーんな\nこれを顔に貼ってライブに来てくれれば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s phosphorescent material~! If all of Kokoro’s fans\ncome to the live with these on their faces…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.9666691621,
      "endTime": 126.19093216259999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.4000024955
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "真っ暗なライブ会場でボォッと浮かび上がる\nファンの顔……すずにゃんのファンより目立たせます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Their faces will faintly glow in the dark live venue…\nI’ll make them stand out even more than Suzu-nyan’s fans!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.4000024955,
      "endTime": 135.102564637,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.3000024955
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "なんですずもこころも\n自分のファンを目立たせる方向性なのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are both Suzu and Kokoro\nfocused on making their fans stand out?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.3000024955,
      "endTime": 140.11961719200002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.3333358288
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……それぞれ個性が出てていいんじゃないかしら\nライブ会場も華やかになりそうだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha… Isn't it nice that their individual personalities are coming through?\nIt will make the live venue more lively.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.3333358288,
      "endTime": 148.5811364651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.7333337147
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "いくら光らしたところで、こころのファンよりも\n私のファンの方が目立ちますわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter how much they glow‚ my fans\nwill still be more noticeable than Kokoro’s fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.7666691621,
      "endTime": 155.0600025018,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
